data.description:
Don't miss out on this 3 bedroom, 2 bath move in ready property with gorgeous upgrades. New A/C, shade screens and shutters throughout. 
Step inside to find a spacious living room flooded with natural light, offering the perfect space to relax or entertain guests. The modern kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, staggered cabinetry, granite countertops, ample counter space, and plenty of storage for all your culinary needs.
The primary bedroom offers a peaceful retreat, complete with an ensuite bathroom featuring all the modern conveniences. The two additional bedrooms are split from primary and share a well-appointed full-size bathroom. 10 foot ceilings, open floor plan perfect for entertaining The meticulously maintained front and backyard boast a new efficient irrigation system, making it easy to enjoy beautiful landscaping year-round, freshly painted garage doors and cozy front and back patio area.  RV gate and plenty of space for parking for car or small boat.
Contact us now to view and experience the true joy of homeownership!
